overview.en: IFCC is a Token Issued by IFC Community to represent the contribution, rewarding those who contribute to the community and IFC. IFCC can be used to decide the development direction of voting Community and IFC.
overview.zh: IFCC是无限币社区发行的一种代表贡献的Token，奖励给为无限币及社区做出贡献的人。IFCC可用于投票决策社区的发展方向及无限币的发展方向。
